{"tid":1398244,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋磚] 全民尋找失物行動","createTime":"2019-08-02T17:37:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T11:43:16.000Z","uid":110501,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2e1d67556ca29505f73a9b20f2b48a7a5b2a6bc9","tid":1398244,"uid":110501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:37:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">目的: </span><br />\n1. 確保第二日<span style=\"color: blue;\">罷工成效</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，造成<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">影響經濟</span></strong></span><br />\n2. 「恢復」將市民出街合法性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3. 成日想和理非變勇武，不如黎次係<span style=\"color: blue;\">勇武變返一日和理非</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屋企個深黃老餅尋日發咗個夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，夢見香港有好多年青人出完夜街唔見咗野，想大家幫手出街搵。咁啱原來出到街都有好多男女老少都<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">搵緊失物</span></span>，貓狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呀、銀包呀、<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">自由</span></span>呀、鎖匙呀、<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">公義</span></span>呀呢啲。咁啱大家都係喺啲多人經嘅地方唔見，即係金鐘、<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">中西環</span></span>、全香港某啲<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">主要幹道</span></span>同埋<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">公共運輸交匯處</span></span>、<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">巴士總站</span></span>、車廠等等。<br />\n<br />\n既然<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">夜晚搵野</span></span>，仲唔知會唔會<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">搵到第二朝返工時間</span></span>，就當然要人人都拎支<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">超強光電筒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>搵啦！萬一有咩<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">黑狗白狗咬人</span>都可以<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">照住佢</span>丫！大家又可以帶啲Memo紙、黃色紙寫住你搵緊乜野，出去貼吓尋物尋貓啟示咁。<br />\n<br />\n因為夢入面成條街好多人都搵緊野，所以<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一定唔係集結</span></span>嘅，聚埋一堆又點搵野呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？最好就<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">分散</span></span>啲，三兩個身位。疏落啲，<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好聚集</span></span>。寧可慢慢搵仔細啲，大不了同一個地方<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">留耐少少</span></span>，唔好走漏眼。不過大家搵極都搵唔到，又唔想放棄，唯有<span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">蓆地而坐</span></span>啦，就咁原地坐低。就算係<span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">路中間</span></span>都冇計啦，大佬真係攰到行唔郁嘛，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔係抖陣恰陣都唔畀呀？</span></span>特別一提嘅係，夢入面果啲又<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勇</span></span>又<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大力</span></span>嘅物主會<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">分得好散</span></span>，咁樣有需要搬搬抬抬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />果陣就<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">梗有一個喺咗近</span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n老餅搵搵吓抖緊果陣無啦啦有差人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，好似唔想比人搵失物咁。大家其實唔洗勞氣嘅，其實佢地一定係出於好心想幫手。呢個時候大家只要接受佢嘅好意，主動<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">同差人講想報失<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>。一個跟一個咁同呀sir講唔見咗啲咩，相信差人一定會合作嘅。如果差人想抬人嘅就仲好，問佢可唔可以<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">幫幫手抬返我去路邊</span></span>，不過希望唔好太多人要抬抬到佢地隻狗咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n最緊要就係大家唔好搵極都搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">塞住啲主要幹道</span></span></strong>搞到第二日唔想罷工嘅人都<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>被迫冇得返工</strong></span></span>啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">人少少罷工對社會冇咩影響，但係如果好多人第二日都返唔到工就</span></span><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">唔係咁</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">好啦！</span></span>雖然搵失物同埋攰得濟坐低抖都<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔犯法</span>，但係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">阻到金融/商業中心運作<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>可能真係會<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">影響經濟</span></span>，咁就好大鑊喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n黎到呢度，老餅個夢就醒咗，朦朦鬆鬆之際喺度口噏噏<br />\n不流血&hellip;<br />\n不受傷&hellip;<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">搵失物都被捕我<strong>屌你老母</strong>&hellip;&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n然後就醒咗去準備<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">八月五日罷工</span></span>了。"},{"pid":"2604e51b8cee528e431cb7a2aeaa8ef4540a6052","tid":1398244,"uid":110501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:38:23.000Z","msg":"8月5號唔返工"},{"pid":"489919518a7ed140ec39be84c06e3e6219053198","tid":1398244,"uid":110501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:38:35.000Z","msg":"8月5號唔返工"},{"pid":"9f31998af7902129d2c5c6647929a1307a915344","tid":1398244,"uid":110501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:38:47.000Z","msg":"8月5號唔返工"},{"pid":"b98865268dc8f035a2e93f9c02e24e0a9da1f2cc","tid":1398244,"uid":110501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:39:00.000Z","msg":"8月5號唔返工"},{"pid":"8863e1e24fd0b8a2b45289d85de3e79e67e8e547","tid":1398244,"uid":110501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:39:23.000Z","msg":"8月5號唔返工"},{"pid":"6c6b6098b6378727aaeadeac1cb286eecd5e723d","tid":1398244,"uid":110501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:39:43.000Z","msg":"8月5號唔返工"},{"pid":"db55dc51cc46199d08f8a02868125e981d7563c4","tid":1398244,"uid":152061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T11:43:16.000Z","msg":"如果我帶屋企隻灰鼠散步，唔小心甩繩走咗入<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">巴士總站</span></span>，大家又好熱心咁幫我入去搵，咁咪出唔到車囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n千祈唔好啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}